elements.name: Registered user creating a new property in the system

steps.name: user will select the required screen as "Create New Property"
he enters property header details as residentialPrivate
he enters owner details for the first owner as bimal
he enters property address details as addressOne
he enters assessment details as assessmentNewProperty
he enters construction type details as defaultConstructionType
he enters floor details as firstFloor
he enters document type details as documentSelect
he forwards for approval to billCollector
he will copy the acknowledgement message with assessment number createProperty-create
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
he forwards for approval to revenueInspector
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
he forwards for approval to revenueOfficer
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
he forwards for approval to commissioner
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
he approved the property with remarks "property approved"
create property details get saved successfully by generating assesssment number
he will copy the acknowledgement message with assessment number createProperty-forward
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
he chooses to act upon above assessment number
